      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaTransmission_header.jpg\" width=\"1407\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/LamaTransmission_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562224&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1407&amp;height=791\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220346/LamaTransmission_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562224&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220376\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaTransmission_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8ec69269-9657-49f0-922b-7b7586ac3169\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/LamaTransmission_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562224&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/LamaTransmission_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562224&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1407&amp;height=791 1x\"></span><p>Translucency is a form of diffuse transmission where light passes through a thin object. This effect is often used to simulate things like leaves, paper, and thin plastics.</p><p><br/></p><h3 id=\"LamaTranslucent-TranslucencyParameters\">Translucency Parameters</h3><p><strong>Color</strong></p><p>This parameter is the resulting color of the surface. You can choose a color or connect a texture or some other procedural pattern.</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>Roughness</strong></p><p>When light passes through a thin object, you may see shadows or silhouettes from the other side. <br/>Roughness can make the light from the other side appear to scatter more or be blurrier.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"af9e8427-ecb6-4abb-978d-39a3e45e5106\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Trans_roughness.0001.jpg\" width=\"264\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/Trans_roughness.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562030&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=264&amp;height=264\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220346/Trans_roughness.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562030&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220373\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Trans_roughness.0001.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0c9f3724-e296-4f06-a6dc-171811f4d7af\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/Trans_roughness.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562030&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=528&amp;height=528 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/Trans_roughness.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562030&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=264&amp;height=264 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Trans_roughness.0002.jpg\" width=\"264\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/Trans_roughness.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562029&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=264&amp;height=264\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220346/Trans_roughness.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562029&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220370\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Trans_roughness.0002.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220346\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6c27458c-875e-42e7-9ac3-82f05f884ab0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/Trans_roughness.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562029&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=528&amp;height=528 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/Trans_roughness.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330562029&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=264&amp;height=264 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Trans_roughness.0003.jpg\" width=\"264\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220346/Trans_roughness.0003.jpg?version=1&amp;m